    "guy_le_pechon_sera_lun_des_deux_animateurs_de": "Guy Le Péchon will be one of the two facilitators for the afternoon dedicated to simulations with role-playing exercises for two Board of Directors meetings.",
    "cet_apres_midi_se_situe_a_la_fin_des_cours_se": "This afternoon session takes place at the end of the courses taking place currently du Certificat de Centrale-Supélec Executive Education for the members en place or potentiels de Comex and Codir.",
