  "page_mentions_legales": {
    "danscette_page_gouvernance_structures_precise": "<span style=\"color: #000099;\">In</span> <b><span style=\"color: #000099;\">this page, Gouvernance &amp; Structures specifies the legal elements relating to its website</span></b>",
    "loi_informatique_fichiers_et_libertes": "<b>Loi informatique, fichiers and libertés</b>",
    "conformement_a_la_loi_du_6_janvier_1978_relat": "In accordance with la loi of 6 January 1978 relative à IT, aux fichiers and aux libertés and à l'article 43 of the loi of 30 September 1986 modifiée, le site a fait l'objet of a déclaration auprès of the Commission nationale IT and libertés (CNIL).",
    "les_utilisateurs_du_site_g_et_s_com_sont_tenu": "Users of the G-et-S.com website are required to comply with the provisions of the Data Protection and Civil Liberties Act, the violation of which is subject to criminal penalties.<br/>They must notably refrain, with regard to personal data they may access, from any collection, any misuse, and in general, from any act likely to infringe the privacy or reputation of individuals.<br/>In accordance with Article 34 of the \"IT and Liberties\" Law No. 78-17 of 6 January 1978, the user has the right of access, modification, rectification and deletion of data concerning them. G &amp; S is committed to complying with the GDPR Law of May 2018. This right can be exercised by sending a letter <a href=\"contact.html\">to our registered office of G &amp; S</a> specifying the nature of the request.",
    "politique_de_g_s_pour_la_gestion_des_donnees_": "<b>G &amp; S Policy on Personal Data Management</b>",
    "lirele_texte_detaille": "Read <a href=\"documents/2022-07-11-texte-RDGP-final-pour-site-G-S.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">the detailed text</a>",
    "utilisation_des_donnees_collectees": "<b>Use of Collected Data</b>",
    "les_informations_telles_que_les_noms_adresses": "Les informations telles that the noms, adresses, … collectées on the site ne feront pas l'objet d'utilisation par G &amp; S autres que celles indiquées on the site. Elles ne sont à aucun moment destinées à être vendues, commercialisées or louées à des tiers.",
    "confidentialite_des_donnees": "<b>Data Confidentiality</b>",
    "les_informations_fournies_par_linternaute_lor": "Information provided by the user, when recorded by G &amp; S, is considered by G &amp; S as not to be disclosed to a third party without the user's consent, but G &amp; S, despite the precautions taken (SSL encryption), cannot absolutely guarantee confidentiality during the internet transmission process of messages. In the event that the user wishes to transmit strictly confidential information, they must contact G &amp; S directly (see <a href=\"contact.html\">contacts</a>).",
    "les_informations_figurant_sur_le_site_g_s_non": "Les informations figurant on the site G &amp; S n'ont pas de caractère confidentiel, Mays ne peuvent être reproduites sans l'accord de G &amp; S (voir Copyright).",
    "responsabilite_de_g_s": "<b>G &amp; S Liability</b>",
    "en_permanence_g_s_fait_tous_ses_efforts_pour_": "G &amp; S constantly makes every effort to ensure that the information presented on its website is accurate, but the user will in no way be able to consider G &amp; S responsible for any inaccuracy or error and will not be able to claim any damages from G &amp; S in the event that such an error has caused them prejudice.",
    "copyright": "<b>Copyright</b>",
    "le_contenu_mis_en_ligne_par_g_s_constitue_une": "The content published online by G &amp; S constitutes a work of the mind within the meaning of the Intellectual Property Code. G &amp; S owns the texts and data, as well as the trademarks, illustrations and graphic elements such as logos, designs and models, or has obtained the right to use them. G &amp; S holds all related intellectual property rights. Any total or partial reproduction of this website and its content, by any means whatsoever, without prior written express authorisation from the company G &amp; S, is prohibited and would constitute an infringement punishable under Articles L335-2 et seq. of the Intellectual Property Code.",
    "liens_internet_vers_g_s_et_reciproquement": "<b>Liens Internet vers G &amp; S and réciproquement</b>",
    "g_s_se_rejouira_de_letablissement_de_liens_in": "G &amp; S se réjouira of the établissement de liens internet pointant vers son site in mesure where hes sont pertinents with his/her activité. Une autorisation formshe is à demander à G &amp; S.",
    "g_s_examinera_avec_attention_toutes_les_deman": "G &amp; S examinera avec attention toutes les demandes d'établisement de lien réciproque. Contacter le <a href=\"mailto:webmaster@g-et-s.com\">Webmaster</a>",
    "cookies": "<b>\"Cookies\"</b>",
    "le_site_g_s_na_pas_de_mecanismes_denregistrem": "Le site G &amp; S n'a pas de mécanismes d'enregistrement de « cookies ».",
    "mentions_legales": "<i class=\"fas fa-gavel me-3\"></i>Legal Notice"
  },
