  "page_administrateur_independant": {
    "criteres_dindependance": "Independence Criteria",
    "lactualite_nannihile_pas_les_ecrits_passes_im": "Current events do not invalidate important past writings",
    "larticle_du_cercle_des_echosexplicite_pourquo": "<a href=\"../documents/2009 11 13 Article des Echos Administrateur qualifié et .. (1).pdf\" style=\"color: white; text-decoration: underline;\" target=\"_blank\">The article in Le Cercle des Echos</a> explains why un independent director within un Board of Directors can act as a vaccine by helping to avoid crises for the company or mitigating them.",
    "un_extrait_du_rapport_bouton_concernant_les_c": "An excerpt from the Bouton Report concerning the criteria for qualifying a director as \"independent\" is recalled here:",
    "pour_plus_dinformations_sur_ce_sujet_nhesitez": "For more information sur ce sujet, n'hésitez pas à nous contacter :",
    "email_contact_g_et_s_com": "<i class=\"fas fa-at text-primary me-2\"></i>\n<strong>Email:</strong> contact@g-et-s.com",
    "ni_mandataire_social_ni_salarie_actuel_ou_au_": "Ni mandataire social, ni salarié actuel (or au cours des cinq dernières années).",
    "ni_administrateur_croise": "Not a \"cross-directorship\" director.",
    "ni_client_fournisseur_ou_banquier_daffaires_o": "Ni client, fournisseur or banquier (d'affaires or de financement) significatif or représentant une part significative de l'activité de la société.",
    "ni_lien_familial_proche_avec_un_mandataire_so": "No close family ties with a corporate officer.",
    "ni_associe_ni_collaborateur_actuel_de_commiss": "Ni associé, ni collaborateur actuel de Commissaires aux comptes (or au cours des cinq dernières années).",
    "ni_administrateur_de_lentreprise_depuis_plus_": "Not a director of the company for more than twelve years.",
    "actionnaires_inferieur_a_10_independant_si_ne": "Shareholders:\n                                <ul style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">\n<li data-i18n=\"page_administrateur_independant.inferieur_a_10_independant_si_ne_participe_pa\">Below 10%: independent if does not participate in control.</li>\n<li data-i18n=\"page_administrateur_independant.superieur_a_10_examen_par_le_conseil_selon_la\">Supérieur à 10 % : examen par le conseil, selon la composition du capital and l'existence de conflits d'intérêts potentiels.</li>\n</ul>",
    "inferieur_a_10_independant_si_ne_participe_pa": "Below 10%: independent if does not participate in control.",
    "superieur_a_10_examen_par_le_conseil_selon_la": "Supérieur à 10 % : examen par le conseil, selon la composition du capital and l'existence de conflits d'intérêts potentiels.",
    "nous_contacter": "<i class=\"fas fa-envelope text-primary me-2\"></i>Contact Us",
    "administrateur_independant_un_vaccin": "<i class=\"fas fa-shield-alt text-primary me-3\"></i>\n                    Independent Director - a Vaccine?"
  },
  "page_apports_ia_compliance": {
    "avant_propos_reflexions_dun_beotien_de_lia_et": "<strong>FOREWORD: REFLECTIONS OF A LAYPERSON ON AI AND COMPLIANCE</strong>",
    "nayant_pas_de_competences_particulieres_sur_l": "Not having particular expertise in AI, I limited myself to writing the foreword that follows.",
    "maintenant_depuis_plus_dune_annee_le_systeme_": "Mayntenant for over a year, le système d'IA « ChatGPT4 » has been made available to the general public. Les grands concepteurs/suppliers de these new services of so-called 'generative' AI, in a ambiance de forte émulation entre eux, ont déployé leur force de frappe marketing. L'effet boule de neige a joué, créant a phenomenon de déferlement. Many people and d'organisations, pas nécessairement qualified, saw an opportunity to make themselves known by speaking out in the media and by publishing articles or books… For the curious layperson that I am, it is somewhat like drinking from a fire hydrant. A few ad hoc searches to find answers to my questions were far from enlightening.",
    "or_la_variete_des_systemes_dia_la_rapidite_da": "Or, the variety of AI systems, the speed at which new tools arrive, the intrinsic difficulty of truly understanding 'how it works', what it can be used for and the risks of wrong turns due to biases are very real obstacles.",
    "une_interessante_approche_possible_consiste_a": "An interesting possible approach consists of starting from examples of AI use in a speciality, such as Compliance, an activity normally known to executives.",
    "aussi_lorsque_en_tant_que_membre_du_comite_sc": "Also when, as a member of the Scientific Committee of the collection Ad Valorem of the Harmattan, I was asked to review this book, je l'ai fait in extenso with interest. J'y ai beaucoup appris, including, on the compliance ! La compliance est observée essentiellement from the perspective of financier, bancaire, fiscal, and also through the lens of la governance and des RH.",
    "bien_des_chapitres_de_cet_ouvrage_sadressent_": "Bien des chapitres de cet ouvrage s'adressent aussi aux décideurs politiques and économiques, aux professionnels de la compliance, du droit and du chiffre, aux ingénieurs en Intelligence Artificielle and aux étudiants and à toutes les personnes s'intéressant à la compliance.",
    "dautres_beotiens_devraient_apprecier_a_la_lec": "D'autres béotiens devraient apprécier à la lecture de ce livre, accessible and agrémenté d'exemples concrets, and y revenir à l'occasion d'une nouvelle interrogation.",
    "accueil": "<a href=\"../index.html\">Home</a>",
    "generalites": "General",
    "apports_de_lintelligence_artificielle_a_la_co": "Contributions of Artificial Intelligence to Compliance",
    "apports_de_lintelligence_artificielle_a_la_co_2": "Contributions of Artificial Intelligence to Compliance"
  },
