  "page_glossaire_prestations": {
    "tant_un_conseil_dadministration_que_des_manag": "Both a board of directors and executive managers may need to use consulting services.",
    "dans_le_cadre_dune_enquete_menee_par_une_equi": "As part of a survey conducted by a team from the <a href=\"https://www.xmp-consult.org/agenda/webinar-intelligence-collective-10196\" style=\"color: #1e73be;\" target=\"_blank\">XMP Consult</a> association, an association of independent consultants from top universities, among such executives, and the publication of the results of this survey in their <a href=\"https://www.xmp-consult.org/global/gene/link.php?doc_id=150&amp;fg=1\" style=\"color: #1e73be;\" target=\"_blank\">annual letter of February 2025</a>, in which G &amp; S contributed two articles, it was deemed useful to include a glossary of consulting services to facilitate the choice between this type of service.",
    "le_resultat_est_larticle_redige_par_g_s_voir_": "The result is the article written by G &amp; S. voir Page 8 <a href=\"https://www.xmp-consult.org/global/gene/link.php?doc_id=150&amp;fg=1\" style=\"color: #1e73be;\" target=\"_blank\">de la lettre</a>.",
    "larticle_propose_une_classification_des_diffe": "The article proposes a classification of the different types of consulting services and for each a summary explaining their content.",
    "quand_un_dirigeant_est_face_a_un_probleme_et_": "When an executive faces a problem and asks themselves which consulting service to call upon to help solve it, quickly reviewing this glossary should provide useful guidance.",
    "images_generees_par_intelligence_artificielle": "Images generated by Artificial Intelligence",
    "pour_plus_dinformations_sur_ce_sujet_nhesitez": "For more information sur ce sujet, n'hésitez pas à nous contacter :",
    "email_contact_g_et_s_com": "<i class=\"fas fa-at text-primary me-2\"></i>\n<strong>Email:</strong> contact@g-et-s.com",
    "nous_contacter": "<i class=\"fas fa-envelope text-primary me-2\"></i>Contact Us",
    "glossaire_des_prestations_de_conseil": "<i class=\"fas fa-book text-primary me-3\"></i>\n                    Consulting Services Glossary"
  },
  "page_historique": {
    "gouvernance_et_structures_propose_aux_conseil": "Governance and Structures propose aux Boards of Directors des services intégrées",
    "communique_de_presse_du_4_mai_2009": "Press Release of 4 May 2009",
    "g_s_pionnier_pour_observation_de_la_feminisat": "<i class=\"fas fa-award\" style=\"margin-right: 10px;\"></i>G &amp; S pionnier pour observation of the feminisation des Boards of Directors",
    "le_communique_de_presse_ci_dessous_indique_la": "Le communiqué de presse ci-dessous indique la reprise par Guy Le Péchon de G &amp; S, cabinet de conseil créé en 2003 par des membres de l'association ADAE",
    "gouvernance_structures_societe_detudes_et_de_": "Governance &amp; Structures, company d'études and de conseil créée en 2003, vient d'être reprise par l'un of his/her associés fondateurs, Consultancy International Services.",
    "desormais_anime_par_son_associe_gerant_guy_le": "DésorMays animé par son associé/gérant, Guy Le Péchon, X-INSEAD, member of the IFA, les « Gouvernance-Advisors » du réseau G &amp; S peuvent mener of assignments très diverses : assessment and « benchmarking » on the fonctionnement or the composition des Boards of Directors en vue d'en augmenter la added value, recherche de corporate officers dont des directors in particular independent, utilisation ad-hoc des nouvelles technologies, enquêtes and études on the « corporate governance».",
    "ainsi_dernierement_g_s_a_mene_une_etude_appro": "Most recently G&amp;S has led an in-depth study on the place of women corporate officers in 550 French companies listed on Euronext, and previously an original survey — at the time — on the topic of \"governance, performance and modernity\", a survey conducted in collaboration with ADAE and the company Acadys among a sample comprising mid-sized companies and subsidiaries of foreign groups.",
    "site_internet_http_www_g_et_s_com": "<strong>Website :</strong> <a href=\"http://www.g-et-s.com\" style=\"color: #1e73be;\">http://www.g-et-s.com</a>",
    "contacts_info_g_et_s_com": "<strong>Contacts:</strong> <a href=\"mailto:info@g-et-s.com\" style=\"color: #1e73be;\">info@g-et-s.com</a>",
    "courrier_guy_le_pechon_g_s_2_allee_des_troene": "<strong>Courrier :</strong> Guy Le Péchon, G &amp; S, 2 allée des troènes, 92330 SCEAUX, France",
    "tel_06_16_31_07_15": "<strong>Phone:</strong> 06 16 31 07 15",
    "g_s_a_ete_le_premier_a_presenter_des_statisti": "G &amp; S has been le premier à présenter des statistiques détaillées on the board gender diversity des listed companies on Euronext Paris, lors of a réunion des anciens of the INSEAD en July 2009 during the temps de préparation of the loi Copé Zimmerman.",
    "letude_g_s_sur_la_place_des_femmes_administra": "L'étude G &amp; S sur <b><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">« La place des women directors in listed companies françaises »</span></b> <span style=\"color: #000000;\">présentée below has been mise à jour à partir des annual reports à fin 2009.</span>",
    "le_petit_dejeuner_organise_debut_juillet_2009": "<span style=\"color: #0033cc;\">The breakfast event organised in early July 2009</span>",
    "par": "<span style=\"color: #0033cc;\"><br/>by</span>",
    "le_club_mixite_et_le_cercle_des_administrateu": "<span style=\"color: #0033cc;\"><br/>le Club Mixité, and le Cercle des Administrateurs<br/>INSEAD ALUMNI ASSOCIATION FRANCE<br/>sur le thème :</span>",
    "la_place_des_femmes_administrateurs_dans_les_": "<br/><b><span style=\"color: #000066;\">\"The place of women directors in French listed companies\"</span></b>",
    "a_rassemble_plus_dune_soixantaine_de_particip": "<br/>brought together more than sixty participants",
    "voir_les_photos_dans_la_colonne_de_gauche": "See photos in the left column",
    "le_theme_a_ete_introduit_par_guy_le_pechon_as": "The theme was introduced by Guy Le Péchon, Associate/Managing Partner of",
    "gouvernance_structures_par_une_presentation_d": "<br/>Governance &amp; Structures by a présentation of results principaux of the étude in-depth qu'he has lede dans plus de 500 French listed companies on the marchés A, B and C d'Euronext",
    "pour_teledecharger_le_programme_de_cet_evenem": "<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">Pour télédécharger le programme de cet évènement</span> <a href=\"./../wp-content/uploads/2020/01/invifad.pdf\">cliquer ici</a><br/><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">Pour parcourir les premiers transparents de la présentation</span> <a href=\"./../wp-content/uploads/2020/01/debpres.pdf\">cliquer ici.</a><br/><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">Pour obtenir des extraits de l'étude, envoyer un courriel à</span> <a href=\"mailto:info@g-et-s.com\">info@g-et-s.com</a> en précisant bien vos noms, prénoms, coordonnées and fonctions",
    "historique": "History",
    "le_petit_dejeuner_organise_debut_juillet_2009_2": "<div align=\"center\">\n<p align=\"center\" data-i18n=\"page_historique.le_petit_dejeuner_organise_debut_juillet_2009\"><span style=\"color: #0033cc;\">The breakfast event organised in early July 2009</span></p>\n<p align=\"center\" data-i18n=\"page_historique.par\"><span style=\"color: #0033cc;\"><br/>by</span></p>\n<p align=\"center\" data-i18n=\"page_historique.le_club_mixite_et_le_cercle_des_administrateu\"><span style=\"color: #0033cc;\"><br/>the Gender Diversity Club, and the Directors' Circle<br/>INSEAD ALUMNI ASSOCIATION FRANCE<br/>on the topic:</span></p>\n<p align=\"center\" data-i18n=\"page_historique.la_place_des_femmes_administrateurs_dans_les_\"><br/><b><span style=\"color: #000066;\">« The place of women directors in French listed companies »</span></b></p>\n<p align=\"center\" data-i18n=\"page_historique.a_rassemble_plus_dune_soixantaine_de_particip\"><br/>brought together more than sixty participants</p>\n<p align=\"center\" data-i18n=\"page_historique.voir_les_photos_dans_la_colonne_de_gauche\">See photos in the left column</p>\n<p align=\"center\" data-i18n=\"page_historique.le_theme_a_ete_introduit_par_guy_le_pechon_as\">The theme was introduced by Guy Le Péchon, Associate/Managing Partner of</p>\n<p align=\"center\" data-i18n=\"page_historique.gouvernance_structures_par_une_presentation_d\"><br/>Gouvernance &amp; Structures through a presentation of the main results of the in-depth study he conducted in more than 500 French listed companies on the A, B and C markets of Euronext</p>\n<p align=\"center\" data-i18n=\"page_historique.pour_teledecharger_le_programme_de_cet_evenem\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">To download the programme of this event</span> <a href=\"./../wp-content/uploads/2020/01/invifad.pdf\">click here</a><br/><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">To browse the first slides of the presentation</span> <a href=\"./../wp-content/uploads/2020/01/debpres.pdf\">click here.</a><br/><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">To obtain extracts from the study, send an email to</span> <a href=\"mailto:info@g-et-s.com\">info@g-et-s.com</a> specifying your full name, contact details and position.</p>\n</div>"
  },
