  "page_questionnaire_rixain_societes": {
    "a_titre_dexemple_voici_deux_premieres_questio": "As an example, here are the first two questions from the questionnaire:",
    "pour_obtenir_le_questionnaire_complet": "To obtain the full questionnaire",
    "lapplication_de_la_loi_rixain_ayant_commence_": "With the application of the Rixain Law having begun, G &amp; S felt it would be very interesting for all stakeholders in the field to have access to the results of a survey of the companies concerned by this Law, in order to understand how they were progressively organising themselves to comply with it.",
    "g_s_a_partir_des_donnees_du_fichier_sirene_de": "G &amp; S à partir des données du fichier SIRENE of the INSEE estime qu'environ mille companies sont in the strict périmètre of the Loi.",
    "g_s_a_elabore_un_questionnaire_et_la_mis_en_l": "G &amp; S developed a questionnaire and put it online. Then, via a mailing, proposed to companies completing it anonymously to subsequently retrieve the survey results in order to benchmark themselves against their peers and obtain ideas to improve their own process for achieving the objectives of the Law.",
    "malheureusement_tres_peu_dentreprise_ont_repo": "Unfortunately, very few companies responded to this questionnaire.",
    "mais_aujourdhui_les_societes_concernees_par_l": "<strong>Mays today les companies concernées by the loi, or souhaitant simplement progresser quant à la feminisation of their governing bodies (COMEX CODIR) peuvent être intéressées à utiliser ce questionnaire comme un autodiagnostic.</strong>",
    "instance_dirigeante": "<strong>GOVERNING BODY</strong>",
    "il_sagit_de_vos_instances_dirigeantes_hors_du": "Il s'agit de vos Instances Dirigeantes hors du Conseil d'Administration or de Surveillance.",
    "votre_societe_peut_avoir_plusieurs_instances_": "Your company may have several governing bodies; for the sake of simplification and consistency in the survey, we ask you to answer the questions about the governing body considered as the main one.<br/>\n                The members of the other governing bodies are part of the group studied further on, in the \"Senior Executives\" section.",
    "quel_est_le_nom_de_linstance_dirigeante_majeu": "<strong>What is the NAME of the main governing body of your company? *</strong>",
    "envisagez_vous_une_evolution_du_nombre_de_mem": "<strong>Do you envisage a change in the number of members of this governing body? *</strong><br/> <em>Only one answer possible.</em>",
    "g_s_enverra_le_questionnaire_en_sa_totalite_s": "G &amp; S enverra le questionnaire en sa totalité sous format PDF aux DG and/or DRH leur en faisant la demande with theurs coordonnées by a courriel à <a href=\"mailto:contact@g-et-s.com\" style=\"color: #1e73be;\">contact@g-et-s.com</a>.",
    "g_s_en_particulier_par_sesgouvernance_advisor": "G &amp; S, in particular through its <a href=\"../gouvernance-advisors/index.html\" style=\"color: #1e73be; text-decoration: underline;\">Governance Advisors</a> specialising in HR and communications, is available to provide advice to companies having to implement the Rixain Law, in particular regarding the planned composition of their Executive Committees or CODIRs and how to build their talent pools.",
    "contactez_nous_avec_vos_coordonnees_pour_rece": "Contact us with your details to receive the full questionnaire in PDF format:",
    "email_contact_g_et_s_com": "<strong>Email:</strong> <a href=\"mailto:contact@g-et-s.com\">contact@g-et-s.com</a>",
    "stable": "○ Stable",
    "reduction_du_nombre": "○ Reduction in number",
    "augmentation_du_nombre": "○ Increase in number",
    "auto_diagnostic_loi_rixain": "Rixain Law Self-Assessment"
  },
